item.title: CVE-2010-3844|2024-08-07T03:26:11.497Z -- ettercap -- ettercap
item.description: An unchecked sscanf() call in ettercap before 0.7.5 allows an insecure temporary settings file to overflow a static-sized buffer on the stack.
